---
---

<div>
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <span class="eyebrow">Process</span>
    <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
      A clear 4-step path
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Each stage removes guesswork and moves you closer to real-team confidence.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative">
    <div class="absolute left-5 top-6 bottom-6 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-[var(--color-accent)]/50 via-[var(--color-accent)]/30 to-[var(--color-accent-2)]/50" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="space-y-0">
      <div class="relative flex gap-5 pb-10">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--color-accent)]/70 bg-[var(--color-surface-0)] flex items-center justify-center z-10 font-mono font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)]">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Start quickly</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted">No coding background needed. Enter the browser lab and begin.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative flex gap-5 pb-10">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--color-accent)]/70 bg-[var(--color-surface-0)] flex items-center justify-center z-10 font-mono font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)]">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Build with reps</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted">Complete guided labs designed around real delivery tasks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative flex gap-5 pb-10">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--color-accent)]/70 bg-[var(--color-surface-0)] flex items-center justify-center z-10 font-mono font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)]">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Pass quality gates</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted">Advance when your work meets practical engineering standards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative flex gap-5">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--color-accent-2)]/70 bg-[var(--color-surface-0)] flex items-center justify-center z-10 font-mono font-bold text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Ship confidently</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted">Finish ready for standups, reviews, and real sprint execution.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto surface-card p-7 text-left">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">How DEVS simulates industry workflow</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm copy-muted">
      You are not just completing lessons. You are practicing a repeatable team
      delivery loop.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm copy-muted">
      <p>✓ Sprint-style planning with scoped tasks</p>
      <p>✓ Review rubric for code quality and readability</p>
      <p>✓ Blocker logging and unblock workflow</p>
      <p>✓ PR feedback loops before “done” is accepted</p>
      <p>✓ Definition-of-done checks before shipping</p>
      <p>✓ Retrospective-style reflection on decisions</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
